{"tid":2178753,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"警方曾向《日經》執行法庭命令　不涉新聞材料和搜查","createTime":"2020-08-28T14:54:43.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-28T15:12:20.000Z","uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"eeea6eb115a61e01144f8baa583c94b9d95bd03d","tid":2178753,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T14:54:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546593-20200828.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546593-20200828.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=7GjM3WQHKJNqnWTuO28XyIsqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=e80a4cb6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1546593-20200828.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=46d4c34d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1546593-20200828.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n《法新社》引述消息報道，警方早前在拘捕壹傳媒創辦人黎智英等人當日，有3名警員持法庭手令，到過《日本經濟新聞》在香港的辦公室。<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆本台查詢表示，本月曾向《日本經濟新聞》執行一份由原訟法庭發出的提交物料令，當中不涉及任何新聞材料，並沒有作出搜查。警方表示，是根據《有組織及嚴重罪行條例》，為偵查一宗「處理已知道或相信為代表從可公訴罪行的得益的財產」的案件。<br />\n<br />\n《日本經濟新聞》公關部回應查詢表示，不評論事件。<br />\n<br />\n據《法新社》報道，消息指警方調查原因是基於《日本經濟新聞》一年前刊登、有關呼籲國際支持香港民主示威的眾籌廣告。有關廣告提及目前已解散的組織「香港眾志」。"},{"pid":"28673f53d682aadc25f4a938ecda35e5eda95a10","tid":2178753,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T14:58:20.000Z","msg":"一年前登廣告關你撚事咩死黑警<br />\n想想廣告收益講成犯罪所得收入？"},{"pid":"1c1525635bf4ef1d407cc64043f7bf282f562098","tid":2178753,"uid":2054,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:01:43.000Z","msg":"即係講中左<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.azquotes.com/picture-quotes/quote-never-believe-anything-in-politics-until-it-has-been-officially-denied-otto-von-bismarck-2-75-80.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.azquotes.com%2Fpicture-quotes%2Fquote-never-believe-anything-in-politics-until-it-has-been-officially-denied-otto-von-bismarck-2-75-80.jpg&h=ef4997f6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2159d6be5ede09d0eb70d99299a09de92d4d19fe","tid":2178753,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:11:25.000Z","msg":"即係搵邊個係登廣告<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n九月份係大清算月"},{"pid":"3590bf1846b4991a405b789601eb4eeb96a104dd","tid":2178753,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"28673f53d682aadc25f4a938ecda35e5eda95a10","tid":2178753,"uid":70786,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T14:58:20.000Z","msg":"一年前登廣告關你撚事咩死黑警<br />\n想想廣告收益講成犯罪所得收入？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-28T15:12:20.000Z","msg":"想<span class=\"red\">將</span>"}]}